    <title>DATA AVAILABILITY</title>
    <p>ProPan is a comprehensive database for profiling prokaryotic pan-genome dynamics (<ext-link xlink:href="https://ngdc.cncb.ac.cn/propan" ext-link-type="uri">https://ngdc.cncb.ac.cn/propan</ext-link>).</p>
